    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上征程，组建一支适应性超群的军队，在这款基于物理引擎的即时战略游戏中，打造出独属于你的战斗风格！在这个新的冰河世纪，珍贵的泽尼特资源引爆了无情的战争，无人能够置身事外。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126360/extras/4434f27c1da92776387480046b223e48.webp?t=1767532237\" width=618 height=35 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126360/extras/0077c380c635b5d58c467a2ad3b5e0f7.poster.avif?t=1767532237\" width=618 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126360/extras/0077c380c635b5d58c467a2ad3b5e0f7.webm?t=1767532237\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126360/extras/0077c380c635b5d58c467a2ad3b5e0f7.mp4?t=1767532237\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126360/extras/422d5fb6db4c26dbe7734bcfab97f273.webp?t=1767532237\" width=618 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126360/extras/ee276a61186eb5e82a6994cbde3bc1dd.avif?t=1767532237\" width=618 height=70 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126360/extras/ad89fec874f09b1773ae9f4a246f5566.webp?t=1767532237\" width=618 height=15 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>定制化军队</strong> ——  从种类繁多的作战单位与部件中进行选择，构建你的钢铁雄狮</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>建造基地、采集资源</strong> —— 建立关键工事，将战略构想付诸行动，深入泽尼特冰原进行开采</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>强化单位</strong> ——  研究尖端科技，因敌制宜地进化你的军队</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>善用兵种</strong> ——  气垫船、机甲、制空火力、步兵部队（包括生化改造人与战斗机器人）尽在麾下，成为你战略战术中的关键力量</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>拥抱真实物理</strong> ——  爆炸产生的冲击、恶劣环境中的碰撞，一切都遵循真实的物理法则诞生</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126360/extras/f2dcdbd0fb9d3324ec20911921bcc6b2.avif?t=1767532237\" width=618 height=70 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126360/extras/ad89fec874f09b1773ae9f4a246f5566.webp?t=1767532237\" width=618 height=15 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>单人剧情模式</strong> —— 亲历跌宕起伏的史诗战役，在扣人心弦的剧情中揭开战争的真相</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>多人匹配对战</strong> —— 在快速匹配或服务器列表中邂逅你的宿敌</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>遭遇战</strong> —— 与人工智能同台切磋，演练战术精进技艺</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>关卡编辑器</strong> —— 赋予创意以实质，设计并分享你的独特关卡</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126360/extras/c35050e433dae258608e64ec17280462.avif?t=1767532237\" width=618 height=70 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126360/extras/ad89fec874f09b1773ae9f4a246f5566.webp?t=1767532237\" width=618 height=15 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2049年，席卷全球的宝贵资源‘泽尼特’已化作人类冲突的导火索。在奈奥斯旧政权倾塌后，凤凰与黯蚀，这两股代表截然不同理念的势力在这新的冰河世纪为了争夺霸权而浴血奋战。黯蚀寻求建立一种不亚于奈奥斯暴政的腐败秩序，凤凰则拼尽全力将其阻挡。不惜一切代价，粉碎黯蚀的野心！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126360/extras/4434f27c1da92776387480046b223e48.webp?t=1767532237\" width=618 height=35 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126360/extras/1dda6e1e81219430f0ac510ef5fb2679.poster.avif?t=1767532237\" width=618 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126360/extras/1dda6e1e81219430f0ac510ef5fb2679.webm?t=1767532237\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126360/extras/1dda6e1e81219430f0ac510ef5fb2679.mp4?t=1767532237\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126360/extras/422d5fb6db4c26dbe7734bcfab97f273.webp?t=1767532237\" width=618 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演一名年轻的指挥官，直面神秘的强敌，引领你的麾下大军阻截敌人势如破竹的攻势，夺回昔日的荣光。这场战争背后潜藏的真相又是什么？一切都等待着你亲自揭晓！</p>",
